      <title>太阳发电飙升将欧洲电力价格低于零</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/solar-generation-surge-sends-european-power-prices-below-zero</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一片晴朗，晴朗的天气增强了整个欧洲部分的太阳能发电，并在中午左右将电价送入负面。]]></description>
