      <title>美联储需要提高“坏消息”降低的威胁。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/el-erian-says-fed-needs-to-raise-threat-of-bad-news-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆罕默德·埃里安（Mohamed El-Erian）称，美联储需要在本周的政策会议上明确表明，如果持续迹象表明经济正在放缓，则可能必须降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/el-erian-says-fed-needs-to-raise-threat-of-bad-news-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:52:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
